{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Netgear |model=WN3500RP |upc=606449087468 |asin=B009MIGCW6 |est_release_date=10/06/2012 |fcc_date=09/09/2012 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=No |manuf=Foxconn |manuf_model=U12H214 |type=extender |fcc_id=PY312300208 |ic_id=4054A-12300208 |pwr_v=100-240 |pwr_conn=AC |cpu1_brand=Broadcom |cpu1_model=BCM5358B0 |ram1=64 |ram1_brand=Winbond |ram1_model=W9751G6JB-3 |expansion_if_types=USB 2.0 |expansion_usb_num=1 |wi1_chip1_brand=Broadcom |wi1_chip1_model=BCM5358B0 |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_ant_conn=U.FL |wi1_txchains=2 |wi1_rxchains=2 |wi1_sstreams=2 |wi2_chip1_brand=Broadcom |wi2_chip1_model=BCM43236B |wi2_802dot11_protocols=an |wi2_ant_conn=U.FL |wi2_txchains=2 |wi2_rxchains=2 |wi2_sstreams=2 |eth_cpu=true |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=1 |flags=DFS, |802dot11_protocols=abgn |default_ssid=NETGEAR_EXT |default_ssid_regex=^NETGEAR_EXT$ |default_ip=192.168.1.250 |default_user=admin |default_pass=password |oui=20:E5:2A |oui_eth=20:E5:2A |default_ch= }} ''Universal Dual Band WiFi Extender''
{{SupportPage|vendor=NETGEAR|model=WN3500RP}} The 5GHz radio is using two '''Skyworks''' ( / '''SiGe''') SE5005L / 5005L power amplifier ICs.
The 2.4GHz radio is using two '''Skyworks''' ( / '''SiGe''') SE2598L / 2598L power amplifier ICs.
There is a '''Wolfson Microelectronics''' WM8955 (WM8955LS) DAC on-board for the 3.5mm audio jack. Per the manual, the default SSID is '''NETGEAR_EXT'''.
